org.eclipse.viatra.dse.genetic.crossovers

Class OnePointCrossover

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.genetic.crossovers.OnePointCrossover
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICrossoverTrajectories

    public class OnePointCrossover
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICrossoverTrajectories
    Makes two child trajectories from two parent trajectories.

    A single crossover point on both parents' trajectories is selected randomly. All transitions beyond that point in either trajectory is swapped between the two parent trajectories. The resulting trajectories are the children.
